@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tgevag(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v1 + 0.13 + v2 + 0.35)))
    v0 = wp.abs((v0 * (tmp + 0.68 / tmp + 0.97)))
    v1 = 0.42
    v1 = 0.35
    tmp = 0.91
    v2 = (v1 - ((tmp + 0.05 - v2 + 0.16) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.34)))
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
